    "strongAgainstReason": "Lylia counters Tank heroes without Blink skills, such as Carmilla and Hylos, who cannot easily escape Gloom's AOE range and are more susceptible to Lylia's high sustained damage.",
    "weakAgainstReason": "Since most of Lylia's damage comes from detonating her 2nd Skill, but setting up Gloom can be quite slow, nimble Assassins like Nolan and Ling counter Lylia as she'll have a tough time hitting them.",
    "synergyReason": "Lylia excels in prolonged battles, and works well with heroes with strong CC, like Franco and Minotaur."
