    "description": "She’s oppressive early because she starts with Shadow Energy charges and can quickly stack Gloom upgrades for high lane control, constant poke, and strong early skirmish DPS. Mid stays strong with Black Shoes enabling reckless trades, but late her damage is more zone/attrition-based and can fall off versus sustained DPS carries and long-range burst if she can’t keep enemies in her detonation area."
